                "S": "<ul>\n\t<li>High school diploma or a letter from your school indicating that you will graduate this year.</li>\n\t<li>A passing grade from the grade 12 Exam for Cambodian citizens.</li>\n\t<li>A passing grade from Paragon International University English Proficiency Test or IELTS 5.5 or TOEFL IBT 60.</li>\n\t<li>A passing grade from Paragon International Univerisity Entrance Exam.</li>\n\t<li>National ID card or passport.</li>\n\t<li>Complete application form.</li>\n\t<li>Four passport-size photos.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<ol>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Exam Form (5 USD)</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Take Scholarship Exam</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Fill out Application Form (10 USD)</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>English Proficiency Test</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Pay Registration Fee (500 USD)</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Freshman Year</p>\n\t</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><strong>All students are required to pay a $500 registration fee at the beginning of each academic year.</strong></p>\n"
