            "admissionRequirement": {
                "S": "<p>To begin their application process students will need to visit our website dmuc.edu.kh and navigate to the apply now page.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Below are the steps in your application process with DMU Cambodia:&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Step 1 - Applying to DMU Cambodia is easy. As a prospective student you can register your interest through our website. Once you have discussed your interest with our Admissions team you will be able to complete the Application Form. There is an Application fee of $100 at this stage.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>The application must include any copies of your passport and all relevant academic transcripts and certificates of English language qualifications or other information required for your application.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Step 2 - Receive an offer. We will log your application and you will receive one of the following decisions by email:&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Unconditional Offer &ndash; you meet the entry criteria. Your place will be reserved until you accept or decline your offer.&nbsp;</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Conditional Offer &ndash; you still need to submit outstanding documents. Your place will be reserved until you meet the rest of the entry criteria.&nbsp;</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Alternative Course &lsquo;Cross-Offer&rsquo; &ndash; based on your qualifications or personal statement, the university thinks you&rsquo;re a better fit for a different, but similar course.&nbsp;</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Unsuccessful &ndash; you do not meet the entry criteria. We will always try and discuss any other options with you where possible&nbsp;</p>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Step 3 - Meet your conditions &ndash; If you are holding an unconditional offer, you have met all the conditions. If you have a conditional offer, then you will need to email your outstanding documents to us. If your offer is conditional on meeting the English language requirements, then you may want to consider a pre-sessional English course at our Centre for English Language Learning.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Step 4 - Accept your offer - To accept your offer you will need to pay a $1500 security fee deposit towards the tuition fees. This demonstrates your commitment to enrolling at DMU Cambodia.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Step 5 &ndash; Welcome to DMU Cambodia! &ndash; we will be available to help you transition quickly and easily into living and studying at our university in Phnom Penh.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Below you will find the entry requirements.&nbsp;</p>\n"
            },
