                "S": "<p>Requirements to Enroll:</p>\n\n<p>Completed application form.</p>\n\n<p>Certificate of National High School Exams/Equivalent certificates.</p>\n\n<p>Copy of Transcripts - Copy of IELTS/TOEFL/Equivalent Proficiency Certificate (if any)</p>\n\n<p>Copy of Birth Certificate/National ID for Locals</p>\n\n<p>Copy of Passport for International Students</p>\n\n<p>4 Recent Passport-size Photographs (at the back side written with name and date of birth)</p>\n\n<p>Application fee ($10) Entrance exams</p>\n\n<p>English proficiency test: IELTS 5.5 for degree entry</p>\n\n<p>- Application &nbsp;Fee =40$</p>\n\n<p>- Administration Fee =2000$(For 4 Years)</p>\n"
