                "S": "<p><strong>1. Admission Criteria</strong></p>\n\n<p>In order to be admitted into the program at CamTech, applicants must submit the following requirements:</p>\n\n<p><em><strong>Local students:</strong></em></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>High school certificate (min. grade D) certified by recognized authority;</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Those who enroll in the Faculty of Engineering, Faculty of Applied Science, and Faculty of Sustainable Built Environment, the grade in Mathematics must be C (minimum);</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Certificate of English proficiency (if any available);</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Any of these: Birth Certificate, valid National Identification Card, or valid Passport;</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>A current passport-size photo (4*6) with white background;</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>A 3-minutes video. The video must be in English which includes:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\t<ol>\n\t\t<li>\n\t\t<p>Self-introduction</p>\n\t\t</li>\n\t\t<li>\n\t\t<p>What is your major or majors of interest? Why did you select this major?</p>\n\t\t</li>\n\t\t<li>\n\t\t<p>Why should the committee select you?</p>\n\t\t</li>\n\t\t<li>\n\t\t<p>What are the advantages and disadvantages of online learning? Any suggestions to improve online learning?</p>\n\t\t</li>\n\t</ol>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><em><strong>International students:</strong></em></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Original high school certificate with transcript&nbsp;(min. grade D);</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Those who enroll in the Faculty of Engineering, Faculty of Applied Science, and Faculty of Sustainable Built Environment, the grade in Mathematics must be C (minimum);</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>A recommendation letter from the school principal or a teacher;</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Passport​ with six months validity to the day arrival in Cambodia;</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Certificate of English proficiency for non-native English speakers (if any available);</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Health certificate (no longer than 6 months);</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>A current passport-size photo (4*6) with white background;</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>A 3-minutes video. The video must be in English which includes:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\t<ol>\n\t\t<li>\n\t\t<p>Self-introduction</p>\n\t\t</li>\n\t\t<li>\n\t\t<p>What is your major or majors of interest? Why did you select this major?</p>\n\t\t</li>\n\t\t<li>\n\t\t<p>Why should the committee select you?</p>\n\t\t</li>\n\t\t<li>\n\t\t<p>What are the advantages and disadvantages of online learning? Any suggestions to improve online learning?</p>\n\t\t</li>\n\t</ol>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong><em>Note:</em></strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>All required documents must be in English. If the original documents are not in English, they must be translated in English and certfied by a recognized&nbsp;institution.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>High school certificate can be submitted when it is required for taking the entrance exam.</p>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Other fees:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Students have to pay 100$ per year for the administration fee. With this fee students will be provided with free internet, library services, and student ID card per annual.</li>\n\t<li>The study materials and other expenses will be covered by students.</li>\n</ul>\n"
