                "S": "<ul>\n\t<li>\n\t<p><strong>Bachelor of Law (English Language Based Bachelor of Law Program-ELBBL)</strong></p>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>&quot; The ELBBL Program is a leading three - year , fully - accredited Bachelor of Law program within RULE . The program is tripartite : coursework , legal research and writing , and practical experience . on the many compulsory areas of law . Its focus on legal research and ELBBL&#39;s curriculum provides a diverse range of classes concentrating writing and robust moot court programs allows students to acquire the skills needed in today&#39;s legal world . This three - pronged mandate , together with its student career services , has made ELBBL one of the most reputable law programs in Cambodia . &quot; - Margaret Ryan , Director of ELBBL</strong></p>\n"
